## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of reflective practice in the UK healthcare system. The studies reviewed may have varying methodologies and sample sizes, which could affect the generalizability of the results. Additionally, the specific impact of reflective practice on UK nurses, as opposed to nurses in other regions, may not be fully captured in the available sources.

